content:
Specify the External System Name and Identifier for Vehicles and Parts.

A Vehicle or an Asset record in the Automotive app can also reside in an external telematics system, an order intake system, or a dealer management system. Use the two new fields Source System Name and Source System Identifier to specify the name of an external system and the ID of an asset or a vehicle in that system.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Automotive is enabled.

Who: Users must have Create access on Vehicle and Asset objects.
